<div class="io-landing-section">
  <h3 id="io-title">IO</h3>

  <div class="io-info">
    <p>Our suite of ever-expanding, industry-standard learning content. Consistently <br> updated with new training content from leading partners in their field.</p>
    <p>Expertly curated for all teams.</p>
    <p>Our essentials suite provides industry-standard best practices, certified by CPD.</p>
    <p>IO is a masterclass in navigating through daily workplace scenarios from Diversity and Inclusion to Health and Safety and Well-being.</p>
