      <h3>400<span class="percent">%</span></h3>
      <p>VR learners are 4x more focused <br> than their e-learning peers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-cta">
      <p id="io-scroll">Explore IO's training offering</p>
      <%= image_tag 'scroll-down', class: "scroll-icon" %>
    </div>
  </div>

